name: User navigates to Free Liters History screen and interacts with the month picker
description: User navigates to Free Liters History and interacts with the month picker.
descriptionHtml: User navigates to Free Liters History and interacts with the month picker.

testStage.description: User navigates to Free Liters History and interacts with the month picker.

steps.name: I get the text "FREE LITERS HISTORY" from the Account Screen
I check that the application text: "FREE LITERS HISTORY" is equals to expected value: "FREE LITERS HISTORY"
I click on "FREE LITERS HISTORY" tab
I get the text "ACCOUNT" header from the Free Liters screen
I check that the application text: "ACCOUNT" is equals to expected value: "ACCOUNT"
I check that the "Back button" is displayed
I get the text "Free liters history" header on Free liters screen
I check that the application text: "Free liters history" is equals to expected value: "Free liters history"
I get default month selected from free liters history screen
I get current month from local calender
I check that the application text: "March" is equals to expected value: "March"
I get month selected after scrolling from free liters history screen
I get current month from local calender
I check that the application text: "February" is not equals to expected value: "March"
